{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-422-sequence-of-points-on-a-hyperbola","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","demoType":null,"title":"Zoezi la 422: Mfululizo wa pointi kwenye hyperbola","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Acha $H$ iwe hyperbola iliyoainishwa na usemi wa hesabu $12x^2 + 7xy - 12y^2 = 625$.</p>\n<p>Zatim, definišite $X$ kao tačku (7, 1). Čini se da $X$ je u $H$.</p>\n<p>Sada ćemo definisati niz tačaka u $H, \\{P_i : i ≥ 1\\}$, kao:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>$P_1 = (13, \\frac{61}{4})$.</li>\n<li>$P_2 = (\\frac{-43}{6}, -4)$.</li>\n<li>Za $i > 2$, $P_i$ je jedinstvena tačka u $H$ različita od $P_{i-1}$, takva da je prava $P_iP_{i-1}$ paralelna pravoj $P_{i-2}X$. Može se pokazati da je $P_i$ jednoznačno određena i da su njene koordinate uvek algebarski brojevi.</li>\n</ul>\n<img alt=\"animation showing defining points P_1 to P_6\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/sequence-of-points-on-a-hyperbola.gif\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Umepatiwa kwamba $P_3 = (\\frac{-19}{2}, \\frac{-229}{24})$, $P_4 = (\\frac{1267}{144}, \\frac{-37}{12})$ na $P_7 = (\\frac{17\\,194\\,218\\,091}{143\\,327\\,232}, \\frac{274\\,748\\,766\\,781}{1\\,719\\,926\\,784})$.</p>\n<p>Pronađite $P_n$ za $n = {11}^{14}$ za sledeći obrazac: Iako je $P_n = (\\frac{a}{b}, \\frac{c}{d})$ gde su delovi u najjednostavnijoj formi i granice su pozitivne, onda je odgovor $(a + b + c + d)\\bmod 1\\,000\\,000\\,007$.</p>\n<p>Kwa $n = 7$, jibu lingekuwa: $806\\,236\\,837$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f5131000cf542c510025","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTop